Overview :

Step 1 — Install Dependencies
pip install torch vision transformers opencv-python scikit-learn pandas seaborn matplotlib

Step 2 — Download Dataset
Unzip the Kaggle dataset in a folder, e.g.:
D:\python\BeiT\archive\chest_xray\test

Step 3 — Run the Main Script
Use the script file:
python beit_pneumonia_pipeline_cleaned.py

Step 4 — Predict and display images 
Predict and display images with labels:
predict_and_show_images(test_image_paths)
